translation: Thou art the Life of all. Thou art the Strength of all. 143.
Thou art in all works. Thou art in all Religions.
Thou art united with all. Thou art free from all. 144.
Salutation to Thee O Destroyer of Hell Lord! Salutation to Thee O Ever-Illumined Lord!
Salutation to Thee O Bodyless Entity Lord! Salutation to Thee O Eternal and Effulgent Lord! 145.
Salutation to Thee O Destroyer of Tyrants Lord! Salutation to Thee O Companion of all Lord!
Salutation to Thee O Impenetrable Entity Lord! Salution to Thee O Non-annoying Glorious Lord! 146.
Salutation to Thee O Limbless and Nameless LordA ! Salutation to Thee O Destroyer and Restorer of three modes Lord !
Salutation tho Thee O Eternal Enity LordA Salutation to Thee O Unique in all respects LordA 147.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਪੋਤ੍ਰੈ, ਨ ਪੁਤ੍ਰੈ ॥ ਨ ਸਤ੍ਰੈ, ਨ ਮਿਤ੍ਰੈ ॥
transliteration: Na Potrai Na Pouttrai|| Na Sattrai Na Mitrai||
translation: O Lord! Thou art Sonless and Grandsonless. O Lord! Thou art Enemyless and Friendless.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਤਾਤੈ, ਨ ਮਾਤੈ ॥ ਨ ਜਾਤੈ, ਨ ਪਾਤੈ ॥੧੪੮॥
transliteration: Na Taatai Na Maatai|| Na Jaatai Na Paatai||148||
translation: O Lord! Thou art Fatherless and Motherless. O Lord! Thou art Casteless. And Lineagless. 148.

gurmukhi: ਨਿ੍ਰਸਾਕੰ, ਸਰੀਕ ਹੈਂ ॥ ਅਮਿਤੋ, ਅਮੀਕ ਹੈਂ ॥
transliteration: Nrisaakan Sareek Hain|| Amito Ameek Hain||
translation: O Lord! Thou art Relativeless. O Lord! Thou art Limitless and Profound.

gurmukhi: ਸਦੈਵੰ ਪ੍ਰਭਾ ਹੈਂ ॥ ਅਜੈ ਹੈਂ ਅਜਾ ਹੈਂ ॥੧੪੯॥
transliteration: Sadaivan Prabhaa Hain|| Ajai Hain Ajaa Hain||149||
translation: O Lord! Thou art Ever Glorious. O Lord! Thou art Unconquerable and Unborn. 149.
